    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> but i would like to seem more test - cases besides \"base under attack\" ...\r\n\r\nIMO the notifications that RA2 provided text for (and which we support) would be an appropriate baseline for this PR.  Considering that this is a user-facing feature we need to either implement a full (or at least self-consistent) set of text notifications, or restrict this PR to plumbing only and not enable anything ingame.  Merging a drastically incomplete set isn't an option."
